definition: and/furthermore/also/together with/(not) at all/simultaneously/to combine/to join/to merge
abbr. for 非洲[Fei1 zhou1], Africa
to not be/not/wrong/incorrect/non-/un-/in-/to reproach or blame/(colloquial) to insist on/simply must

sentences.english: Although solitary accessory spleen is not uncommon, multiple accessory spleens are rare.
sentences.chinese: 虽然单一性副脾并非不常见，但多发性副脾仍属少见。

sentences.english: The existing vaccines can only reduce the amount of virus, rather than totally inactivating it.
sentences.chinese: 当前的疫苗只会减少病毒数量，并非真正杀灭病毒。

sentences.english: Not all products might have the same route through the supply chain.
sentences.chinese: 并非所有产品都沿着相同的路径通过供应链。

sentences.english: But such data has not been forthcoming from the countries of the region.
sentences.chinese: 但是这样的数据在该地区的各国并非唾手可得。

sentences.english: Naturally, the process of coming up with this list wasn't always easy.
sentences.chinese: 当然，拿出这份书名目录的过程中并非总是很容易的。

sentences.english: This is a preview, not the V1 release.
sentences.chinese: 这依旧是一个预览版，并非V1版。

sentences.english: However, high-producing lines that express these genes are not generally available.
sentences.chinese: 但是，表达这些基因的高产品系并非随处可得。

sentences.english: Brown is right on with his handicapping of the situation.
sentences.chinese: 布朗的理解也并非不正确。

sentences.english: For non-batch programs, stopping the collector forever is not an option.
sentences.chinese: 对于非批处理程序，永久停止收集器并非好的选择。

sentences.english: People will pay for access to those in a way they won't for the latest episode of House or a reality show.
sentences.chinese: 人们付费来阅览的并非是一段议会的插曲或现实秀。

sentences.english: The two best-known gene culprits weren't causing her dystonia.
sentences.chinese: 两个最知名的基因元凶并非导致她肌张力障碍。

sentences.english: Life is not a dream, destiny is held in our own hands.
sentences.chinese: 浮生并非若梦，命运还靠自己把握。

sentences.english: Examples of demonization of homosexuality is not unique in history.
sentences.chinese: 将同性恋妖魔化的事例在历史上并非绝无仅有。

sentences.english: Raj: Y've been a sucky friend, a sucky, sucky friend.
sentences.chinese: 听着，我承认我并非一直是个称职的朋友。

sentences.english: But not all advertisements are trustworthy.
sentences.chinese: 但是，并非所有的广告都真实可靠。

sentences.english: Not all properties are appropriate for all versions of queue manager.
sentences.chinese: 并非所有属性都适合于所有版本的队列管理器。
